{"tid":1137883,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國馬拉松支持環保走塑.  派發可食用Ooho水球代替20萬膠樽","createTime":"2019-05-04T06:47:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-04T07:52:39.000Z","uid":41343,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"38adf321f01a2e0810c96ffdbbd0ce9b72b3f0bb","tid":1137883,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T06:47:19.000Z","msg":"每逢舉辦馬拉松或大型跑步比賽，主辦單位都會大量派發樽裝水或運動飲品給選手們，令活動結束時產生大堆塑膠垃圾。而英國倫敦上年馬拉松統計一共丟棄超過90萬個膠樽，引起關注活動環保問題。今年4月舉辦的馬拉松帶頭減廢減塑行動，向選手派發「可食用水球」代替膠樽，成功較上年減少了20多萬個膠樽。<br />\n英國倫敦2018年馬拉松就一共丟棄超過90萬個膠樽，引起關注活動環保問題，去年倫敦就禁止半馬拉松使用一次性即棄水樽。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有英國公司Skipping Rocks Lab製作可食用水袋Ooho，由海藻萃取物製成薄膜，再注入水或運動飲品。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n選手可以將整個Ooho直接食用，或是咬開飲用然後丟棄水袋，水袋可以在六星期內自然分解。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/w600/201905/20190503122715_1_6-1024-1024.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2Fw600%2F201905%2F20190503122715_1_6-1024-1024.PNG&h=01907caf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/topic/w600/201905/20190503122718_3_40382399-1171827609662115-1929416360106917888-n-1024-600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Ftopic%2Fw600%2F201905%2F20190503122718_3_40382399-1171827609662115-1929416360106917888-n-1024-600.jpg&h=a2ed3cd1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"955aee6604b4e0ed6c40085019ef674d1de8fb83","tid":1137883,"uid":142499,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T06:57:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0ef6bede6ba66a9e8224fdab5ba1ed4645bb0ff6","tid":1137883,"uid":52090,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T07:06:02.000Z","msg":"呢d先叫進步同有建設性"},{"pid":"39027f982ce7a1a9301f212e541f920b25090b4d","tid":1137883,"uid":52215,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T07:09:51.000Z","msg":"十年後，發現水袋含有致癌物<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe58749233691bfbb392b6762e67c4e7880fcfcd","tid":1137883,"uid":188,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T07:10:41.000Z","msg":"有冇塞住海龜個鼻<br />\n冇就算啦"},{"pid":"85ba0f90fba3760b822df2f6401b2eb1f40f4c19","tid":1137883,"uid":193642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T07:11:42.000Z","msg":"幾好"},{"pid":"36c1e64337e834b30b2559ee3381d167c95ce18b","tid":1137883,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T07:17:54.000Z","msg":"成本？"},{"pid":"cfd0481df2e64fea116d937c8e8f7e74727a99ef","tid":1137883,"uid":209391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe58749233691bfbb392b6762e67c4e7880fcfcd","tid":1137883,"uid":188,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T07:10:41.000Z","msg":"有冇塞住海龜個鼻<br />\n冇就算啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T07:19:20.000Z","msg":"塞六星期<br />\n六個禮拜後自然分解<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a334187e74435f4ab1503a3f256b4f40ebcf4f79","tid":1137883,"uid":32706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T07:52:39.000Z","msg":"將啤酒塞入去"}]}